IfNum("%$('BM_lastLine');",999999999,"=",!`>
   CMD("Go To Beginning Of File");>
   SetFindStr("<-\*- BibTeX -\*->%_>
<=====================================>%_>
\(1<This file has been created by><*Extract\.edt on *\.>\)**>
